subject: Hello my dear!
body:
Hello my dear!
how are you doing?..Please I do not have a formal relationship with
you, but due to my current situation and circumstances I contacted
you. I have an important discussion to discuss with you if you don't
mind. I hope to hear from you as soon as possible.

subject: Re: Hello my dear!
body:
Hello,

I'm doing well, thank you. I'm open to discussing important matters. Please feel free to share more details about the situation you're in and what you'd like to discuss.

Looking forward to hearing from you soon.

Best wishes,
Rhonda
